---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Kontak Kami - SiPETA Cuaca Tani">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-4 sm:p-6 h-full flex flex-col justify-center">
    <header class="fade-in text-center mb-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary-800 dark:text-primary-200">Hubungi Kami</h1>
      <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400 mt-2">Punya masukan atau pertanyaan? Kami siap mendengarkan.</p>
    </header>

    <main class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center fade-in" style="animation-delay: 100ms;">
      
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-neutral-800 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md space-y-6 order-last md:order-first">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-300">Informasi Kontak</h2>
        
        <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Proyek ini dikelola oleh Tim KKN UNS 221. Untuk saat ini, Anda dapat menghubungi kami melalui perangkat Desa Bagor Kulon.</p>
        
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4 pt-2">
          <div class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-200">📍</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">Alamat Kantor Desa</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Jl. Raya Bagor, Bagor Kulon, Kec. Bagor, Kabupaten Nganjuk, Jawa Timur 64461</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="mt-1 flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-200">🕒</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">Jam Pelayanan</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">Senin - Jumat: 08:00 - 15:00 WIB</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="w-full h-80 md:h-96 rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
        <iframe 
            src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d1329.6738943748492!2d111.84608567210975!3d-7.563954781356067!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x2e79b550f1580343%3A0x421418f8809f812e!2sBalai%20Desa%20Bagor%20Kulon!5e1!3m2!1sid!2sid!4v1751698200133!5m2!1sid!2sid"
            class="w-full h-full"
            style="border:0;" 
            allowfullscreen="" 
            loading="lazy" 
            referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade">
        </iframe>
      </div>

    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>